WEBVTT

00:01:28.404 --> 00:01:30.531
I, too, thought I was brave.

00:01:31.459 --> 00:01:32.863
But I wasn't.

00:01:34.894 --> 00:01:38.446
I had simply never before experienced

00:01:39.085 --> 00:01:41.325
true fear.

00:01:42.737 --> 00:01:43.913
That changed

00:01:45.246 --> 00:01:47.627
on February 23, 2002.

00:01:49.246 --> 00:01:52.526
At the time, I was a presidential
candidate in Colombia

00:01:53.209 --> 00:01:56.557
promoting my campaign agenda,

00:01:56.581 --> 00:01:59.814
when I was detained
by a group of armed men.